#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid "vortex stone"
msgid_plural "vortex stones"
msgstr[0] "涡流石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vortex stone'}
#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid ""
"This is a stone with spirals all over it, and holes around its perimeter.  "
"Though it is fairly large, it weighs next to nothing.  Air seems to gather "
"around it."
msgstr "这是一块布满螺旋纹路、边缘有孔洞的石头。虽然体积相当大，但重量却轻如无物。空气似乎会聚集在它周围。"

#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid "spiral stone"
msgid_plural "spiral stones"
msgstr[0] "螺旋石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spiral stone'}
#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid ""
"A rock the size of your fist.  It is covered with intricate spirals; it is "
"impossible to tell whether they are carved, naturally formed, or some kind "
"of fossil."
msgstr "一块拳头大小的石头。表面覆盖着复杂的螺旋纹路，无法分辨是雕刻而成、自然形成还是某种化石。"

#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid "blob glob"
msgid_plural "blob globs"
msgstr[0] "粘液团块"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blob glob'}
#: .\blaze_override.json
msgid ""
"A little hunk of glop that fell off a blob monster.  It doesn't seem "
"hostile, but it does wiggle occasionally."
msgstr "从粘液怪物身上脱落的一小团粘稠物。它似乎没有敌意，但偶尔会扭动。"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid "crystal path"
msgstr "水晶路径"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid "diamond obelisk"
msgid_plural "diamond obelisks"
msgstr[0] "钻石方尖碑"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid "diamond prism"
msgid_plural "diamond prisms"
msgstr[0] "钻石棱镜"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid ""
"A tall tower composed almost entirely of diamond, the cluster of diamond "
"matrices focuses the energy from an array of solar panels into a terribly "
"powerful laser.  It is also capable of storing energy from the sun and can "
"fire even in the dark."
msgstr "一座几乎完全由钻石构成的高塔，钻石矩阵簇将太阳能电池板阵列的能量聚焦成威力极强的激光。它还能储存太阳能，即使在黑暗中也能发射。"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid "single"
msgstr "单发"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgctxt "gun_type_type"
msgid "launcher"
msgstr "发射器"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid ""
"A smaller crystal that fell off the diamond obelisk upon creation.  Through "
"some unknown mechanism, is able to link with the obelisk to fire a small, "
"yet still powerful laser.  Even more perplexing is its ability to do so "
"without guidance."
msgstr "钻石方尖碑生成时脱落的小型晶体。通过某种未知机制，它能与方尖碑连接，发射虽小但威力强大的激光。更令人费解的是，它无需引导即可做到这一点。"

#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid "diamond matrix"
msgid_plural "diamond matrixs"
msgstr[0] "钻石矩阵"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'diamond matrix'}
#: .\blaze_vortex_diamonds.json
msgid ""
"A sparkling diamond with a dazzling spiral pattern.  Small pieces of "
"glittering crystal form on the edges as you hold it.  With enough base "
"material, applying it to objects causes organic matter, wood in particular, "
"to rapidly transform into diamond. However, this new crystalline compound "
"quickly disintegrates without some other form of support."
msgstr ""
"一颗闪耀着炫目螺旋图案的钻石。当你手持时，边缘会形成细小的闪光晶体。若有足够的基础材料，将其应用于物体可使有机质（尤其是木材）迅速转化为钻石。然而，这种新的晶体化合物若无其他形式的支撑会快速分解。"

